5. so anything that‚Äôs selected will have changed its color

#file style.css
P::selection{
    color: rgb(1, 183, 1);
    background-color: rgb(176, 173, 173);
}


6. we add an item in front of the text 
we will add a checkmark before any list
select id fruit and then select all li tag within id fruit
then add some style for the item

#file style.css
#fruit li::before{
    content: "‚úî";
color: tomato;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
}

this would be better
